Asheville.William E. Breese Sr. House:
William E. Breese Sr. House is a historic house located at 674 Biltmore Avenue in Asheville, Buncombe County, North Carolina.


== Description and history ==
It was built in 1891 by architect Charles B. Leonard, and is a 2 1/2-story, rectangular timber-framed dwelling in the Queen Anne style.
